    {
      "id": "PopularPost317594",
      "post_content": "So I decided to add 3 to my Esper deck, in which I want to play [Inquisition of Kozilek](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inquisition of Kozilek) and [Thoughtseize](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thoughtseize) on my turn or [Spell Pierce](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Pierce)/[Brainstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brainstorm) on theirs. I'll come back with the results.  \n  \nEDIT: Wonderful, just wonderful. It's a B mana the turn you play it and a U mana on theirs. As simple and useful as that. Play a land to produce a B with it and If it ends up being your only U source in play, don't worry, you will be extra careful with the timing of your next land drop.",
      "posted_by": "CG1248",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost317594\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">So I decided to add 3 to my Esper deck, in which I want to play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Inquisition of Kozilek\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inquisition of Kozilek\">Inquisition of Kozilek</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thoughtseize\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thoughtseize\">Thoughtseize</a> on my turn or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spell Pierce\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spell Pierce\">Spell Pierce</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Brainstorm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brainstorm\">Brainstorm</a> on theirs. I'll come back with the results.<br/><br/>EDIT: Wonderful, just wonderful. It's a B mana the turn you play it and a U mana on theirs. As simple and useful as that. Play a land to produce a B with it and If it ends up being your only U source in play, don't worry, you will be extra careful with the timing of your next land drop.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '317594'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy94702\">CG1248</span>\r\n                                (5/25/2013 12:44:54 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRat